{"tid":1060540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】夫妻現身幼稚園零交流 呂慧儀黃文廸早已貌合神離","createTime":"2019-03-13T22:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:27:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad218d073e712eb4eaf6371ea827133326f67dd","tid":1060540,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:01:12.000Z","msg":"呂慧儀與黃文廸於11年結婚，婚後3年誕下兒子Anton，可惜最後敵不過七年之癢。黃文廸早前被《蘋果》踢爆在巴士上和一名女子有親暱舉動，在新歡新聞曝光的當晚深夜，兩人更隨即發出共同聲明，表示2018年已由夫婦變回朋友關係，又強調離婚跟第三者無關，兩人日後會共同撫養兒子。（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2TBmtbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TBmtbs&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=57939179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2TBmtbs</a> ）<br />\n《蘋果》讀者陳小姐昨日透過「爆相爆片」，披露去年11月曾在幼稚園遇到呂慧儀與黃文廸，當時已發覺二人貌合神離，直至最近得知原來二人早已離婚，即恍然大悟。陳小姐的小朋友和呂慧儀的兒子在屯門區同一間幼稚園上課，當日他們一起出現，皆因是觀課日，讓父母觀察子女上課及老師教學狀況，陳小姐說：「當時都未知離婚，見到佢哋一齊坐，但好奇怪，完全冇交流，呂慧儀不停撳電話，兩個人一句嘢都冇講過。」<br />\n雖然當時正值流感高峯期，所以家長們都需要戴上口罩，但陳小姐表示一眼就認得出他們：「平時都好少撞到呂慧儀，多數係佢老公送小朋友返學放學，上年K1到今年K2，小朋友都係返半晝，成日見到佢老公接仔放學，一接完就即刻走，冇同家長有咩交流，只係覺得佢好得閒，好似唔使返工咁。至於呂慧儀，就冇撞過佢嚟接個仔。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552472291_75eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552472291_75eb.jpg&h=0bdfb034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552472339_eca4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552472339_eca4.jpg&h=606d5b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190313/large/1552472340_5637.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190313%2Flarge%2F1552472340_5637.jpg&h=779d059e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190314/59364577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F59364577&d=ctOUxKLv%2B9zBCrzB%2FMEnrZmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=64c3622d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190314%2F59364577&h=542469ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190314/59364577</a>"},{"pid":"0a1f784d1854e5ad4e1182fb40405db5cf55e19f","tid":1060540,"uid":181822,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:06:23.000Z","msg":"第二張相咁似送殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ae9839bac4e96d066f00506a15812ed8587e69","tid":1060540,"uid":87598,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:21:34.000Z","msg":"陳小姐都幾八婆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edd40bfba198f803655666e0358e4c082b49533","tid":1060540,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a1f784d1854e5ad4e1182fb40405db5cf55e19f","tid":1060540,"uid":181822,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:06:23.000Z","msg":"第二張相咁似送殯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T22:38:26.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a6cdd11fb8f0d874931d7b596aa535cfdc0f09","tid":1060540,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T23:04:27.000Z","msg":"第一眼都以為係<br />\n<br />\n黑色衫 紅色摺櫈 黃色布幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087109d4d5581982a05d2c4962768633bc0667fe","tid":1060540,"uid":173617,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T23:13: